The '''Binks & Son Whaling Company''' was a [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] whaling company that operated out of [[Otoh Gunga/Legends|Otoh Gunga]]. It lasted for [[Standard century/Legends|centuries]], during which the [[Binks family]] had developed a tradition of sailing the seas, often traversing the entire [[Naboo/Legends|world]].

